In Situation @[0B5D]
assume $X$ is integral and has genus $g$.
Let $\mathcal{L}$ be an invertible $\mathcal{O}_X$-module.
If $\deg(\mathcal{L}) \geq 2g$, then $\mathcal{L}$
is globally generated.
